{
  "_comment": "Phase 5 / VFX_ASSETS WS-A + A4 hero GLBs. Every hero in an enabled KayKit cohort (Knight/Mage/Barbarian/Rogue) ships its own CC0 base, tri-tone palette-retextured to its three-color identity (recolorMode \"tritone\": the atlas is gradient-mapped in texture space — shadow->secondary, midtone->primary, highlight->accent — so the result reads multi-tone instead of a flat factor wash; build_assets.mjs) and trimmed to the clips the animator drives. Raw bases live in tmp/asset_src/kaykit (gitignored); only the optimized output under public/assets/heroes is committed. No-budget policy (DECISIONS 2026-06-13): one file per cohort hero, storage is not a constraint.",
